@startuml
title Activity Diagram: RAG Query - Ask AI About Project

|User|
start
:Navigate to project page;
:Enter question about project;
:Click "Ask AI" button;

|System|
:Validate project has SRS document;
if (SRS document exists?) then (no)
  |User|
  :Show error: "Please upload SRS document first";
  stop
else (yes)
  |System|
  :Convert question to embedding vector\n(via OpenAI API);
  :Search similar chunks in Supabase\n(project_vectors table);
  :Retrieve top-K relevant documents;
  if (Relevant chunks found?) then (no)
    |User|
    :Show message: "No relevant information found";
    stop
  else (yes)
    |System|
    :Combine context chunks;
    :Generate answer using LLM\n(with retrieved context);
    |User|
    :Display AI answer;
    :Option to ask follow-up question;
    stop
  endif
endif

@enduml

